Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:06.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:09.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:17.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kamaitachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:25.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The theory we bring this time is a second edition
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:26.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:27.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:34.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 2nd If someone close by is dishing out good gossip, you'll forget work and be stuck in place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:38.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Had to do a 2nd one quickly \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the first one hasn't been aired yet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:41.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:45.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it had been, then no one would fall for it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:46.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Your explanation is very accurate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:48.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But that said, the first time this guy really sat there completely motionless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:49.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:56.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The show's AD had a relationship with an actress
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.75,0:01:00.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We tested how long he'd stay there listening
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:01:07.61,special_Wed_1_X,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an1\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(408,836)}The topic of the relationship between the AD and the actress of the TV drama without saying the name to keep him there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:01.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He listened especially carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:03.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really listened very carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:07.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With program staff waiting for him to join a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unbelievably he was there for 16 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:13.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I waited for so long, but they did not say the name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:16.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who was it? It was hidden in such a roundabout way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:21.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't sleep with ADs that talk like this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:25.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What does everyone think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:26.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you encounter this situation in a cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:31.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the TMC lounge, there's a kind of curtain that separates
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can hear everything the person next to you says. \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:40.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Once an idol asked her agent "Please let me stop blogging"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:41.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I really want to stop" like that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:45.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I did listen there without moving a muscle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:47.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On a side note
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:49.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamaye mistakenly entered the women's room at TMC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:53.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Screams of the Hinatazaka46 member's could be heard from outside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:54.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is really off-topic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:55.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Off-topic indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:01.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The gossip challenge returns again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:02.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to be a "Troublemaker" YouTuber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:08.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If a child says "I want to be a YouTuber who gets into trouble"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:12.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No parent will say "Since it's your choice..." and show their support
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This theory will be tested
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:39.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Once again, if someone close by is dishing out good gossip, you'll forget work and be stuck in place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:47.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, we also called the verification target to the coffee shop inside TBS under the name of a fake meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:51.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,While there, the meeting location changes and they are informed they need to get there as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:56.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will they continue to stay and listen to the neighboring gossip?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okubo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:05.98,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will definitely listen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of gossip do you plan to use this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:17.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A classic topic like female ADs having sex with celebrities
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:21.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's cut to the chase and start the gossip
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:29.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I went to a hotel with a comedian some time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Comedian?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's bad, right? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who is it? Which comedian?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:37.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still considered very popular
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:38.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems to be listening a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do not tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I won't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.23,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Gradually approaching \N-Sitting position changed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:47.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, it was cheating
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Head up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:54.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After hearing the keyword "cheating", her eyes change
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:04:00.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time the tactic of naming the person is adopted
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:06.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like I'd say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Hitori
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:08.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:11.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hitori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:15.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait a minute I'm a little confused
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:18.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Gekidan Hitori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:18.89,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't use my name without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:19.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:20.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's bad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really, Hitori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Look at her face
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:22.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is clearly a sigh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:27.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Obviously shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.07,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was a blow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:31.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably thinking, "Even Hitori?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now it is especially troublesome
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:34.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:38.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because he has more than one lover
