Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.26,0:24:46.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Great! Thank goodness it's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.83,0:24:49.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this theory, can you guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.83,0:24:53.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Having an affair will make your heart pound?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.40,0:24:55.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is no such theory
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.51,0:24:57.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of stupid theory is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.14,0:25:00.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Great! Thank goodness it's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.71,0:25:02.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is not true, of course, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.88,0:25:05.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it's more important to hurry up and get to the meeting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.48,0:25:07.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.72,0:25:10.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You turned your phone off so there was nothing we could do
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.92,0:25:11.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.18,0:25:15.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, in first place was Ogata
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.40,0:25:18.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With over 9 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.36,0:25:21.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And probably had no intention to go to the meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.65,0:25:25.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you all think?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.27,0:25:28.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ogata's developed very unexpectedly
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.35,0:25:29.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.31,0:25:30.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ogata's wasn't finished
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.85,0:25:32.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He followed them out
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.41,0:25:36.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We should have kept it going
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.75,0:25:38.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next theory could have been
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.15,0:25:41.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many kilometers will he follow them for
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.01,0:25:45.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I have personally heard these rumors about Mrs. Ogata
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.09,0:25:45.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh-
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.26,0:25:47.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's a big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.24,0:25:48.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There aren't any, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.56,0:25:50.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ogata will pursue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.92,0:25:52.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed \N -Constantly following Matsumoto
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.01,0:25:57.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome the next presenter
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.44,0:26:06.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Koyabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.54,0:26:10.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So let's get right to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.48,0:26:14.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does anyone watch Youtube?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.98,0:26:18.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The sound is too loud to hear anything
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.27,0:26:20.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is there still a ceiling for hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.02,0:26:22.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just hear "bang!"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.06,0:26:23.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.86,0:26:26.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I will watch comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.56,0:26:28.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Their online shows \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.63,0:26:31.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also watch some YouTube channels
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.44,0:26:34.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada doesn't watch YouTube, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.01,0:26:36.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, i'm the same, I have a look from time to time
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.39,0:26:41.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To see what other guys who have retired are up to now
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.65,0:26:44.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's what you like to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.12,0:26:47.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That sort of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.29,0:26:48.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Social type
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.78,0:26:52.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What "social type"? He's the "anti social" type
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.34,0:26:56.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The theory I bring today is about YouTube
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.66,0:27:06.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No parent would say "Since it's your choice..." to support a child who says "I want to be a trouble-making YouTuber"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.44,0:27:13.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think, especially those of you with children?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.24,0:27:14.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You won't support it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.82,0:27:18.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's strange, isn't it, to emphasize "troublemaker"?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.51,0:27:23.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'd just want to ask "why"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.02,0:27:27.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Imagine your child looking at you with a straight face, what you would say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.12,0:27:29.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Blunt eyes, right?\N  -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.65,0:27:32.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Since it is your choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.36,0:27:34.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can say it.\N  -No, no, no, no, no
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.93,0:27:47.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No parent would say "Since it's your choice..." to support a child who says "I want to be a trouble-making YouTuber"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.42,0:27:57.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first parent-child pair is Saito and his 18-year old son
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.78,0:27:58.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.93,0:28:00.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The parents divorced shortly after birth
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.39,0:28:07.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He lives with his mother in Aomori and is in his fourth year of high school
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.59,0:28:02.76,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since they saw each other
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.23,0:28:08.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Some things are better to say directly
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.49,0:28:12.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I've seen a live skit.\N  -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.10,0:28:14.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since we had a separate live\N  -Last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.12,0:28:15.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, nothing since then.\N  -Ohhhh
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.03,0:28:18.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very interesting.  \N-That's great
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.64,0:28:21.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No sound at all, my throat was so dry
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.28,0:28:27.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After a long absence of father and son alone together, Saito speaks in his home dialect
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.45,0:28:28.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,After this they'll start talking
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.49,0:28:33.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time to see a live show
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.11,0:28:38.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Saito is called to the hotel where he was staying on the pretext that there was something important to discuss
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.92,0:28:41.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you want to talk about, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.93,0:28:44.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm in fourth grade now. \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.15,0:28:47.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just think it's time for me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.33,0:28:50.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's time to think about the future.\N  -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.75,0:28:52.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you about this
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.27,0:28:55.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With me?\N  -Yes, yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.41,0:29:00.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you want to work, you have to come here.\N  -It's true
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.11,0:29:03.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, what I want to do is
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.28,0:29:05.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Be a trouble-making YouTuber
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.95,0:29:08.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Straight to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.22,0:29:10.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.82,0:29:11.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really really really
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.88,0:29:14.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?\N  -Serious, serious
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.18,0:29:15.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.38,0:29:18.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You may think that being an ordinary YouTuber is enough
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.06,0:29:20.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why don't you be a regular YouTuber?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.70,0:29:23.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why a trouble-making one?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.43,0:29:25.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tell me why you wanna be a troublemaking YouTuber specifically
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.79,0:29:28.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you do ordinary things...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.53,0:29:31.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of YouTubers now, right? \N -Yes, a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.50,0:29:35.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's why they say, "is this channel like so-and-so's"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.29,0:29:36.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But its the same for troublemakers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.17,0:29:41.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Has anyone been arrested recently for being a troublemaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.27,0:29:43.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I  haven't seen much YouTube
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.51,0:29:44.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen much?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.88,0:29:48.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Especially troublemaking YouTubers, I hate them the most
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.85,0:29:52.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't tolerate making money by causing trouble to others
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.69,0:29:55.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, to be honest, now I'm very, very shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.50,0:30:00.31,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A dependable father
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.31,0:30:01.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In response to his son's declaration that he would "get into trouble in the future"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.11,0:30:04.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Saito is very shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.97,0:30:04.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very good, very good
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.71,0:30:07.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Let's say for example
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.68,0:30:09.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're going to do it after you graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.20,0:30:10.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, I think it's fine to start now
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.54,0:30:13.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not going?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.32,0:30:15.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're not going to school?\N  -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.42,0:30:18.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's not worth it. I mean it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.24,0:30:20.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it is necessary to do immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.05,0:30:23.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you have to do it in Tokyo, I understand completely
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.29,0:30:24.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.12,0:30:29.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can I come here after I graduate from college?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.36,0:30:31.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I won't support you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.42,0:30:33.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm saying it straight it up front. \N -Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.69,0:30:35.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To convince Saito
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.62,0:30:42.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, a specific plan to cause trouble is proposed
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.61,0:30:44.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.87,0:30:46.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You know that type of exposure fetish?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.05,0:30:49.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll go out wearing that kind of long coat
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.45,0:30:52.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then suddenly open it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.38,0:30:54.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But inside i'm actually wearing ordinary clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.71,0:30:56.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can just do that as a skit!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.82,0:30:57.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.99,0:31:00.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scaring people is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.73,0:31:05.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hurting someone is something you can't afford to do
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.30,0:31:07.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although there's actually nothing bad going on in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.56,0:31:09.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Watching from the side might be funny
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.30,0:31:12.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But from the perspective of the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.97,0:31:14.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You are scaring her either way
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.13,0:31:16.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Young women or children, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.14,0:31:18.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Never do it to children
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.20,0:31:19.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.65,0:31:23.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The father will definitely be worried about this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.11,0:31:28.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sexual pranks against children is not a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.26,0:31:32.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even if you're not a father, you'd be right to say that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.76,0:31:35.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I need to reply to an email... Oh, no, a LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.90,0:31:39.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm really worried to hear you say this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.09,0:31:40.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a cut!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.67,0:31:42.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So boring
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.71,0:31:46.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I want to become this troublesome type either way
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.67,0:31:47.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.03,0:31:49.15,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The son is very strong willed
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.91,0:31:49.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.57,0:31:50.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good or bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.90,0:31:54.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's bad, i'm very hesitant
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.01,0:31:56.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see it, and don't support it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.05,0:32:00.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Saito said no completely
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.12,0:32:02.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, we revealed the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.29,0:32:07.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.45,0:32:08.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.40,0:32:10.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.86,0:32:12.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.90,0:32:16.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So annoying, I said such embarrassing things
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.51,0:32:20.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kid says "I want to be a trouble-making YouTuber"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.23,0:32:24.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The theory is that no parent would say "Since its your choice..." and show support
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.24,0:32:26.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.21,0:32:27.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who would support it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.94,0:32:30.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to beat him up
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.81,0:32:33.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I'm divorced and separated again
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.61,0:32:34.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So its unconvincing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.75,0:32:36.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's great that I was denied
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.93,0:32:39.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because I did not expect a refusal to such an extent
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.22,0:32:40.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's great. That's really great
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.19,0:32:42.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For sure!  \N-From the bottom of my heart, I feel glad
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.37,0:32:45.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A good kid, actually
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.04,0:32:47.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next parents and children who participated in the verification were
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.00,0:32:53.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,KUDOU MIKIKO, an entertainer, and her father
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.41,0:33:01.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,KUDOU went to Waseda University and started to work as a comedian at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.77,0:33:10.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But she didn't tell her father about becoming an comedian initially as she thought he would be "absolutely opposed"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.57,0:33:15.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A father who seems to be against even "comedy"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.52,0:33:19.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What will be his reaction to "trouble-making"?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.97,0:33:23.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's time to consider employment.\N  -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.64,0:33:28.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've thought about what I want to do so this is not really a discussion
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.44,0:33:30.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Informing me? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.38,0:33:31.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.77,0:33:36.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Troublemaking YouTuber...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.84,0:33:39.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Want to be?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.55,0:33:43.66,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,But still calm
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.69,0:33:44.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.42,0:33:45.90,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Gentle Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.68,0:33:47.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that the "troublemaker" type?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.74,0:33:53.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eating in the supermarket but not paying for the food, stuff like that to attract attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.59,0:33:55.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.17,0:33:57.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will not do criminal things
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.60,0:33:59.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you going to live on this for the rest of your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.57,0:34:01.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think its pointless
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.58,0:34:04.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A bit sad
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.35,0:34:06.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it good for others and society?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.74,0:34:09.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's the reason you want to go for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.42,0:34:10.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Or is it just because it makes money?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.84,0:34:15.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the audience finds it interesting, it's good
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.48,0:34:17.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't support it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.92,0:34:23.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't support this kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.90,0:34:26.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As expected, he was opposed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.80,0:34:29.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.90,0:34:35.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought you would support what I wanted to do
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.40,0:34:40.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Why don't you let go and support me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.64,0:34:46.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Facing the father who does not support her dream
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.92,0:34:48.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She can't help but shed a tear
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.50,0:34:51.27,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a bit off
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.76,0:34:53.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}You want to make it your life's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.22,0:34:55.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.35,0:34:59.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You only live once. \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.01,0:35:00.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Dad's heart is softened because of the tears
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.37,0:35:02.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Well...it's not bad to try
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.40,0:35:05.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will try it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.20,0:35:12.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, he reluctantly agrees to her becoming a troublemaking YouTuber
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.69,0:35:11.53,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mixed emotions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.26,0:35:16.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, the mother and sister come home
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.37,0:35:22.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here, she explains the specific project she intends to do
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.99,0:35:25.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a live camera of Enoshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.55,0:35:30.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shooting the beach of Enoshima
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.53,0:35:33.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The one that was on the weather forecast. \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.13,0:35:38.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll draw a big poop on the beach there like this
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.22,0:35:40.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.32,0:35:40.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.63,0:35:44.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm still trying to decide whether to paint it or write it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.37,0:35:45.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Cute project
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.95,0:35:46.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Painting is better\N  -Is it better to paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.84,0:35:49.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why not draw a dog too?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.59,0:35:51.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pooping dogs and poop
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.56,0:35:50.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Making recommendations
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.34,0:35:57.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eventually, even advice is given from the "troublemaking family"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.44,0:36:00.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, we reveal the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.63,0:36:01.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.40,0:36:04.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.16,0:36:07.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.07,0:36:12.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'll agree if they want to try it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.47,0:36:14.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, it can not be helped
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.33,0:36:19.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you don't let her do it, she'll regret it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.77,0:36:22.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't want to give her such regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.45,0:36:28.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After confirming that the father "wants to support his daughter's dream"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.08,0:36:32.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She decides to disclose her comedy activities
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.06,0:36:33.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still needs to say this
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.30,0:36:38.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Comedian \N-Want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.79,0:36:40.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Would love to be
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.46,0:36:43.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now I have an agent
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.94,0:36:47.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From time to time, I also participate in live events
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.33,0:36:50.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? You've become busy
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.68,0:36:53.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That I would totally support you in\N  -Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.17,0:36:54.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.02,0:36:56.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)} Really? \N-Funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.98,0:36:59.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.71,0:37:03.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What to do if you don't do what you want to do once in a lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.88,0:37:05.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Dad is so nice
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.95,0:37:11.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kudou shed tears of joy in the face of her father's tenderness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.03,0:37:13.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This technique
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.39,0:37:16.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First leading with "Troublemaker YouTuber"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.37,0:37:19.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course you'd be relieved to hear "comedian" afterwards
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.20,0:37:21.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Being a comedian isn't such a bad thing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.31,0:37:22.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.74,0:37:25.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have a great pair of parents
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.04,0:37:30.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is Honahonami, who has 2 years of experience, and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.73,0:37:31.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of name is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.12,0:37:36.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Her father, who also doesn't know that his daughter is a comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.53,0:37:37.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Haven't even told your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.03,0:37:38.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.69,0:37:42.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Getting into trouble, you'll be scolded, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.02,0:37:44.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And you'll be called a criminal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.10,0:37:45.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Won't do criminal things
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.79,0:37:47.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then you are really in the abyss
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.48,0:37:52.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No matter how she tries to persuade, he does not approve
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.20,0:37:52.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.44,0:37:57.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Being a comedian will be talked about at the point of the reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.25,0:38:03.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I started working as a comedian 2 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.82,0:38:08.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After graduating from college, I want to live as a comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.45,0:38:10.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is even scarier
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.93,0:38:12.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it okay? To be a comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.86,0:38:15.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Well... if you think it's your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.76,0:38:20.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As long as it does not cause trouble for others, its fine
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.94,0:38:21.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The standard has dropped a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.13,0:38:24.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This side also reluctantly agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.42,0:38:29.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The final parents and children who participated in the validation were
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.78,0:38:36.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nichokenju's Kobori and his son
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.49,0:38:40.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Won't Downtown open a Youtube channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.02,0:38:41.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.08,0:38:43.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can detail your daily lives
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.13,0:38:44.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada wants to do one about driving his wife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.44,0:38:46.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That'd be weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.59,0:38:48.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are also couples who drive together
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.64,0:38:49.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.37,0:38:51.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.86,0:38:54.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, I heard you have something to say
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.16,0:38:56.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here's the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.84,0:38:58.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? Whoa, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.97,0:39:00.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Want money?\N  -Not money
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.77,0:39:02.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't have the money
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.50,0:39:05.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is about the future
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.44,0:39:08.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I found what I wanted to do
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.24,0:39:10.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you about this
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.23,0:39:12.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you wanted to be a teacher at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.68,0:39:14.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Previously, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.59,0:39:18.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now I want to be a troublemaking YouTuber
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.20,0:39:22.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.66,0:39:24.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to be that kind of person?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.44,0:39:26.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Want to be a YouTuber I can still understand a little
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.07,0:39:29.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? What... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.36,0:39:31.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Troublemaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.13,0:39:36.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Facing a big turn in direction from "education" to "trouble-making"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.21,0:39:38.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kobori is very upset
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.35,0:39:41.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'll be scolded and arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.58,0:39:44.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I wont do illegal things
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.21,0:39:46.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is to get popular by causing trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.82,0:39:48.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to cause trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.61,0:39:50.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why do this kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.56,0:39:52.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Working as a teacher is good
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.53,0:39:54.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is a YouTuber who causes trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.79,0:39:59.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even this trash who is well known for his cheating and debts
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.77,0:40:04.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does not approve of activities that cause trouble for others
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.41,0:40:07.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, why do you want to be that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.81,0:40:09.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why not? There's nothing wrong with it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.85,0:40:11.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should know...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.80,0:40:17.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've been called "scum" and "trash"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.00,0:40:19.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Originally?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.76,0:40:21.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then my son is causing trouble everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.06,0:40:23.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I wonder what else will be said
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.45,0:40:25.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I just want to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.23,0:40:27.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, although there are many YouTubers
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.46,0:40:29.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They don't have love!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.39,0:40:30.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No love?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.09,0:40:31.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, those guys
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.41,0:40:32.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Saying that all you need is popularity
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.95,0:40:36.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The troublemaker type means you don't care what happens to others
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.94,0:40:40.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not funny and no love
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.47,0:40:44.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This kind of thing ... there is no need to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.35,0:40:47.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What type of things do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.42,0:40:52.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now, some examples of projects are given
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.42,0:40:57.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For example, if it's related to a comedian  \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.06,0:41:02.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I buy all the tickets of comedian's live show
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.87,0:41:06.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then on the day 0 people show up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.48,0:41:06.93,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very bad
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.87,0:41:08.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's funny about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.57,0:41:10.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.20,0:41:12.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who would find it interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.23,0:41:15.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its a prank to see the reaction of the person
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.44,0:41:19.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then does the comedian feel they benefit too?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.00,0:41:22.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its publicity for them too
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.16,0:41:24.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the end, it is a win-win situation
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.72,0:41:26.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's nothing funny about failure to comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.51,0:41:27.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.29,0:41:30.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you understand the feelings of a comedian when they are pranked like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.73,0:41:32.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.38,0:41:35.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,YouTubers ignore many rules
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.23,0:41:38.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They think "it's good to be scolded"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.44,0:41:40.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hate people like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.85,0:41:45.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He sounds like he's just talking about himself
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.23,0:41:47.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's mad at his own company \N-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.15,0:41:49.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who are you trying to screw, for example?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.78,0:41:53.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For example, COWCOW
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.54,0:41:56.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.08,0:41:57.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why COWCOW... we are the same generation
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.71,0:42:01.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because we're the same generation we have a good relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.45,0:42:06.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That Tada can't take a joke
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.40,0:42:08.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's always having a go at me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.89,0:42:10.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tell me to "go and talk about Manzai".
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.77,0:42:11.76,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tada will be furious
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.60,0:42:13.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tada takes good care of me too
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.20,0:42:18.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kobori does not look like he is going to agree at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.98,0:42:23.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are also seniors in the university doing this
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.64,0:42:28.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They did something over the top and are now super popular
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.52,0:42:32.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can earn about 1 million a month
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.65,0:42:35.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Non-pro?\N  -Yeah, a million
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.14,0:42:35.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Interested
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.84,0:42:38.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Talking about money...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.26,0:42:42.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,1 million, 1 million
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.12,0:42:45.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll give you half, or more
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.20,0:42:48.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Half for Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.03,0:42:49.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Say you don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.48,0:42:51.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Getting motivated
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.58,0:42:51.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The wind direction has changed
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.81,0:42:55.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If I have 1 million a month, I can give you 600,000
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.98,0:43:01.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,College tuition will be paid for, too
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.45,0:43:00.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now he's thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.21,0:43:03.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course, I can also supplement the family
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.78,0:43:05.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now just 1 million
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.82,0:43:09.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Doing YouTube, 2 million 3 million is also possible
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.11,0:43:10.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, want to do it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.16,0:43:14.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.25,0:43:17.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have a reputation
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.26,0:43:20.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You being in it it'll surely be popluar
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.54,0:43:23.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Eh... \N -3 million
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.71,0:43:25.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What will you do with the 3 million you earn?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.33,0:43:26.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shaken by money
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.40,0:43:32.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 18-year-old has lured his father with enticing potential
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.45,0:43:38.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can also come up with ideas, it'll surely be popular
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.12,0:43:40.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In that case, its the same as your comedy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.96,0:43:41.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Trying hard to convince!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.38,0:43:45.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're also doing music
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.55,0:43:48.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Trying to DJ \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.42,0:43:49.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't it the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.66,0:43:54.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What did Kobori ultimately conclude?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.57,0:43:56.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.64,0:43:58.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Not…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.14,0:44:00.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can understand a little if I am a YouTuber
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.67,0:44:04.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But causing others trouble and controversy like this
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.75,0:44:07.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't say I agree. Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.75,0:44:08.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Disagree?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.84,0:44:09.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Disagree
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.35,0:44:14.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kobori stopped at the last step
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.43,0:44:17.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the truth was revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.71,0:44:19.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,When it comes to money he almost agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.50,0:44:22.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What what what what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.99,0:44:24.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, this is fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.99,0:44:26.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.57,0:44:28.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You've already got staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.27,0:44:31.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A team is formed? What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.06,0:44:34.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, we explained the project
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.54,0:44:37.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wednesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.47,0:44:38.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.77,0:44:41.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're working with Wednesday?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.64,0:44:43.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With Downtown?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.54,0:44:46.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.73,0:44:47.40,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's so shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.99,0:44:50.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Fooled by my own child...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.26,0:44:56.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H3732FF&\c&HFFFFFF&}In summary\N{\r}I want to see what the parents of trouble-making YouTubers are like
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.90,0:44:59.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.20,0:45:05.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The examples of troublemaking are still relatively cute and mild
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.01,0:45:08.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are also fathers who agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.12,0:45:11.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you give bad kind of examples then they will certainly be opposed
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.22,0:45:12.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.20,0:45:16.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But this show itself is a trouble-making variety show
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.15,0:45:20.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If a child says, "I want to be a staff member of Wednesday Downtown"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.35,0:45:23.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The parents will certainly be worried
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.00,0:45:24.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Are you okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.68,0:45:27.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Can't you just go to a regular variety show?"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.84,0:46:14.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks for watching. Support me and get subs early at patreon.com/zwanster03

